Notes: UWO ranked 15th in the NCAA Div. III...UWL's Anderson scores 16 points, her
team's final eight...UWL's Atchison scores a career-high 28 points, including
nine in overtime...UWL's Cramer sends forces overtime with three-pointer with
three seconds left...UWO's Schmidt forces 2 OT on 2 FTs with 2 seconds left.
Game.Officials: Tim Duffy,  Wesley Porter,  Ron Quirk
